  "texts": [
    "We find the generated QAs are quite good and only do small effort in correction.",
    "To get the data of Temporal Description, we directly parse the syntactic structure of the questions according to the time signal words \"before/after/when/while\".",
    "Specifically, we keep the question part ahead of the time words.",
    "For instance, we derive the new question \"what did the person do?\"",
    "from the original question \"what did the person do after she took the black item away?\""
  ],
